Description: Network-level YouTube brainrot video filter for Linux
 BrainrotFilter is a transparent network proxy that analyzes YouTube
 videos using keyword matching, scene detection, audio analysis, and
 engagement metrics. It integrates with Squid proxy to intercept and
 filter YouTube traffic on your network.
 .
 Features include:
  - Real-time YouTube video analysis
  - Configurable detection thresholds
  - Web-based admin dashboard
  - Squid SSL bump integration
  - iptables transparent proxy setup
  - Community keyword sharing
